Minister what steps he is

2006705019
00:03:29.066 --> 00:03:32.202
taking and the frontbench
team is taking to strengthen

310357944
00:03:32.203 --> 00:03:34.660
safeguarding in the family
courts and to protect

171456494
00:03:34.661 --> 00:03:37.400
domestic abuse survivors
from retraumatization,

1159656387
00:03:37.401 --> 00:03:41.657
particularly where perpetrators use
mechanisms such as child contacts,

4058802522
00:03:41.707 --> 00:03:43.611
arrangements to continue their abuse.

1250245765
00:03:43.612 --> 00:03:50.349
>> Josh Dean well, the whole House
will have sympathy for Olivia.

2796166365
00:03:50.351 --> 00:03:52.952
The family courts must
never be a place for

1546525407
00:03:52.953 --> 00:03:54.857
perpetrators to continue their abuse.

2176603370
00:03:55.755 --> 00:03:58.260
Repealing the presumption
of parental involvement

4145522372
00:03:58.261 --> 00:04:00.415
will ensure children's wellbeing continues

2404672683
00:04:00.416 --> 00:04:03.706
to be the court's primary
focus when considering

733024573
00:04:03.707 --> 00:04:06.059
contact and under
the child focussed model,

115480960
00:04:06.060 --> 00:04:09.256
independent domestic violence
advisors can provide

631705481
00:04:09.257 --> 00:04:12.105
victims with specialist family support.

230540306
00:04:12.106 --> 00:04:14.161
