2370360749
00:04:22.110 --> 00:04:25.463
Two thirds of families who use
that scheme avoid going to

92631982
00:04:25.464 --> 00:04:29.505
court takes a lot of pressure
off the family courts.

2399523162
00:04:29.506 --> 00:04:30.509
It started in 2021.

1905460926
00:04:30.510 --> 00:04:33.360
It gets renewed every
year, often at the end of

389851732
00:04:33.361 --> 00:04:36.108
