>> Thank you, Mr.

3089448825
00:05:28.569 --> 00:05:29.019
Speaker.

1127508991
00:05:29.020 --> 00:05:31.327
Reach out and recover
Ken through a brilliant

871526512
00:05:31.328 --> 00:05:32.982
