that we're currently seeing

1996277987
00:08:00.211 --> 00:08:03.707
and ensuring their obligations
to equality are met?

3595599432
00:08:03.708 --> 00:08:04.409
>> Ministers.

3634079917
00:08:04.410 --> 00:08:07.303
>> She's absolutely right
to raise the importance

957836320
00:08:07.304 --> 00:08:08.758
