into phase two work for the sections

3422193150
01:47:44.265 --> 01:47:47.406
north of Birmingham before
they were abruptly cancelled.

272011137
01:47:47.407 --> 01:47:50.959
Huge contracts were handed out
without improvement in price.

2247847479
01:47:50.960 --> 01:47:55.057
Despite the Oakervee
review's recommendation

3158597760
01:47:55.058 --> 01:47:56.661
to negotiate a better position.

888566159
01:47:57.857 --> 01:48:00.161
Instead of signalling
the country's ambition,

2129010855
01:48:00.163 --> 01:48:03.560
HS2 became a symbol of this country's

3842033182
01:48:03.561 --> 01:48:07.366
decline and after more than five years of

1748194223
01:48:07.366 --> 01:48:09.812
construction and over £40 billion spent,

1511901132
01:48:09.813 --> 01:48:14.068
the country was no closer
to having an operational

2848165107
01:48:14.069 --> 01:48:18.159
HS2 railway than when
construction first began.

3988670183
01:48:18.160 --> 01:48:20.661
That is the shocking
legacy of the previous

988874201
01:48:20.663 --> 01:48:24.460
government and I am afraid it gets worse.

536429283
01:48:24.461 --> 01:48:30.113
I can today confirm the previous
government spent most of

2668655367
01:48:30.114 --> 01:48:33.210
his Budget without laying
a single metre of its track.

1624091270
01:48:33.211 --> 01:48:37.909
Today is about ending that era of neglect.

1678253050
01:48:37.910 --> 01:48:41.703
New CEO Mark wild
and chair Mike Brown have

1610965019
01:48:41.704 --> 01:48:44.507
an almost impossible task on their hands.

3725306614
01:48:44.508 --> 01:48:46.064
As Mark put it to me recently,

825575392
01:48:46.065 --> 01:48:53.455
it's like changing the engine
of an aeroplane mid-flight.

582663933
01:48:53.457 --> 01:48:57.973
However, the new leadership team
at HS2 is turning things around.

1528311395
01:48:57.975 --> 01:49:01.058
Six major construction
milestones were reached

820983626
01:49:01.059 --> 01:49:03.411
earlier than planned in the past year.

3676708075
01:49:03.411 --> 01:49:07.857
The organisation is more focussed
on the things that matter,

2982267251
01:49:07.859 --> 01:49:11.334
with 300 back office roles removed,

2015197265
01:49:11.335 --> 01:49:15.610
HS2 limited is reviewing its supply
chain contracts and the incentives

1035193317
01:49:15.611 --> 01:49:20.318
within them to ensure we finish
the job at the lowest reasonable cost.

1461840371
01:49:20.856 --> 01:49:25.658
And it is managing those
contractors properly now to

2374604226
01:49:25.659 --> 01:49:28.308
make sure supplier performance
is up to scratch.

3541688036
01:49:28.309 --> 01:49:33.818
Finally, we are seeing
improved oversight with HS2

2580546468
01:49:33.819 --> 01:49:36.307
leadership now receiving
real time updates,

3365473489
01:49:36.308 --> 01:49:40.962
helping to prevent delays
and keep construction to time.

977212389
01:49:40.963 --> 01:49:43.518
But there is no getting
away from the fact, Mr.

1754354135
01:49:43.518 --> 01:49:49.661
Speaker, that the vast majority of
Hs2's previous Budget was blown on,

1735056488
01:49:49.663 --> 01:49:53.766
completing around a third
of the entire project.

4107472654
01:49:53.767 --> 01:49:56.607
And over the past year.

238980199
01:49:56.609 --> 01:50:01.014
Mark Wild and HS2 limited
have worked closely with me

3155881779
01:50:01.015 --> 01:50:05.419
and my department to assess
the remaining work to be done.

3658852778
01:50:05.420 --> 01:50:09.411
They have now provided
me with updated costs

1862876870
01:50:09.411 --> 01:50:12.192
and timescales which I can
share with the house.

3217001026
01:50:12.193 --> 01:50:17.310
It gives me no pleasure
to say the expected

2755104954
01:50:17.311 --> 01:50:23.762
cost of completing HS2
is now between £87.7

4200567116
01:50:23.763 --> 01:50:28.663
billion and £102.7
billion, priced in 2025.

3225581178
01:50:28.664 --> 01:50:32.512
Two thirds of this
increase is down to past

3335419339
01:50:32.513 --> 01:50:36.364
misunderstanding of the work required.

973412165
01:50:36.365 --> 01:50:38.368
Underestimation and inefficiency issues

4056417856
01:50:38.369 --> 01:50:40.264
within the control of HS2 limited,

1761011063
01:50:40.265 --> 01:50:44.621
some of its suppliers
and previous governments.

2849909942
01:50:44.622 --> 01:50:48.217
The remaining third is linked to
inflation, which was not factored

1370878809
01:50:51.860 --> 01:50:55.310
into previous cost estimates
regularly enough on timings.

249216659
01:50:55.311 --> 01:50:57.320
I said last year that I see no route by

237123962
01:50:57.893 --> 01:50:59.848
which trains could be running by 2033.

1823300963
01:50:59.850 --> 01:51:07.561
We now expect first services to run
from Old Oak Common to Birmingham

1761347392
01:51:07.562 --> 01:51:10.561
Curzon Street between May
2036 and October 2039,

2157793763
01:51:10.562 --> 01:51:14.821
and where the previous
government could not say when.

2398931118
01:51:14.822 --> 01:51:16.627
The full HS2 scheme between Houston

1439764919
01:51:16.628 --> 01:51:18.783
and Handsacre Junction would be delivered.

2461055568
01:51:18.784 --> 01:51:25.813
I now expect that will happen
between May 2040 and December 2043.

4283569120
01:51:25.814 --> 01:51:28.669
Lessons have been learned
from the Stewart Review,

4110801819
01:51:28.670 --> 01:51:32.561
meaning hs2's cost and schedules are

2691803223
01:51:32.562 --> 01:51:34.417
now built on more solid foundations,

362525491
01:51:34.418 --> 01:51:36.964
with credible estimates
published as ranges to

3575102358
01:51:36.966 --> 01:51:40.666
ensure they better stand the test of time.

2723455056
01:51:40.667 --> 01:51:43.625
Colleagues may feel that they've
heard all of this before,

1234487028
01:51:43.627 --> 01:51:49.411
and I understand that scepticism,
but it is different this time.

1683114248
01:51:49.411 --> 01:51:53.259
HS2 limited have now used the same experts

2561691054
01:51:53.261 --> 01:51:55.817
and methods behind
the successful Crossrail reset.

4204518742
01:51:55.818 --> 01:51:59.214
They have priced future work
against what we've learned so far,

1173660498
01:51:59.214 --> 01:52:04.318
and their homework has been checked
by an independent panel of experts.

2346014375
01:52:05.860 --> 01:52:10.259
But Madam Deputy Speaker,
if this seems like an obscene

1767735297
01:52:10.261 --> 01:52:12.720
increase in time and costs,
it is because it is.

1970796842
01:52:13.819 --> 01:52:18.566
And if it seems like I'm
angry, it is because I am.

2058952124
01:52:18.567 --> 01:52:22.620
I am angry on behalf of taxpayers
and affected communities who have been

2918821149
01:52:22.621 --> 01:52:25.878
swindled by the failures of
successive conservative governments.

968933729
01:52:27.861 --> 01:52:31.022
I am angry on behalf of
the thousands of rail and construction

168501724
01:52:31.023 --> 01:52:33.311
workers giving their all on this project,

283322570
01:52:33.312 --> 01:52:37.484
who do not deserve to have their
industry tarnished in this way.

253106409
01:52:37.485 --> 01:52:41.966
And I am angry on behalf of
passengers who continue to wait

2397029459
01:52:41.967 --> 01:52:46.074
for the new services and new
opportunities they deserve.

906124729
01:52:46.075 --> 01:52:49.166
Madam Deputy Speaker, despite
this sorry situation,

2714955240
01:52:49.167 --> 01:52:54.816
we are determined to claw back as
much time and money as possible.

1470348723
01:52:54.817 --> 01:52:57.810
Not only does the Lovegrove
report corroborate

3590543587
01:52:57.811 --> 01:52:59.815
the Stewart Review's damning assessment

1409712553
01:52:59.816 --> 01:53:03.124
of the decision making environment
under the previous government,

287284965
01:53:03.125 --> 01:53:08.368
but it also talks about
the original gold plating of HS2.

1069423344
01:53:08.369 --> 01:53:12.418
It talks about the focus and I quote,
on the highest possible speeds,

369250938
01:53:13.820 --> 01:53:18.264
resulting in bespoke
and highly engineered design.

4095054820
01:53:18.265 --> 01:53:22.212
Madam Deputy Speaker to translate,
it was a massively overspent folly,

2321229684
01:53:22.213 --> 01:53:25.414
with the prospect of
the fastest trains anywhere in

674121984
01:53:25.415 --> 01:53:28.714
the world tickling the fancy
of conservative Ministers.

630820353
01:53:28.714 --> 01:53:30.110
If we were the.

2475274264
01:53:30.111 --> 01:53:32.119
If we were a country the size of China.

1140953083
01:53:32.120 --> 01:53:34.913
I could understand it.

874396890
01:53:34.914 --> 01:53:35.717
But we are not.

3000818804
01:53:35.718 --> 01:53:38.419
Passengers just want reliable trains that

46388499
01:53:38.420 --> 01:53:40.911
turn up when they're supposed to.

2545517974
01:53:40.913 --> 01:53:42.417
More services and more seats.

1496476314
01:53:42.418 --> 01:53:45.532
They want a common sense approach that

84247729
01:53:45.533 --> 01:53:48.168
gets them the railway they deserve,

4053739084
01:53:48.169 --> 01:53:52.172
not a vanity project with trains
so fast that proper testing could

78244687
01:53:52.173 --> 01:53:58.368
not be done until track
and railway systems were complete.

3117528526
01:53:58.369 --> 01:54:01.365
So, Madam Deputy Speaker,
I asked Mark Wilde to remove

2960442454
01:54:01.366 --> 01:54:05.566
the gold plating
and complexity from this project.

3213649748
01:54:05.567 --> 01:54:11.066
Today I have accepted his
recommendation to align

2982750083
01:54:11.067 --> 01:54:13.222
HS2 speeds already delivered with already,

276666648
01:54:13.223 --> 01:54:17.366
with speeds already delivered on
other European high speed networks.

2799188681
01:54:17.368 --> 01:54:21.417
That still means we will run some
of the fastest trains in Europe,

3831366410
01:54:23.821 --> 01:54:25.324
with speeds reaching 320km/h.

851307397
01:54:25.325 --> 01:54:29.426
But crucially, it lowers
the cost of testing.

807027255
01:54:29.427 --> 01:54:32.068
It makes delivering
the project less risky,

2000090288
01:54:32.069 --> 01:54:36.372
and it could realise savings of up to £2.5

52416453
01:54:36.373 --> 01:54:41.570
billion and could save at least
a year in delivery time.

521126259
01:54:41.571 --> 01:54:45.131
Now I realise that there will
be those who will say this is

1284812608
01:54:45.132 --> 01:54:50.219
all too much and we should
just cancel the whole thing.

3819521440
01:54:50.220 --> 01:54:53.464
However, I can confirm today
that it could cost almost

2909312121
01:54:53.466 --> 01:54:56.566
as much to cancel the line
as it would to finish it,

3790646275
01:54:56.567 --> 01:54:59.366
while delivering none of the benefits.

1968911370
01:54:59.366 --> 01:55:03.471
With half finished structures strewn
across the English countryside,

143705750
01:55:03.472 --> 01:55:05.720
a relic to what could have been.

588398608
01:55:05.721 --> 01:55:11.169
And so this Labour government
is clear we will deliver HS2

336992484
01:55:11.170 --> 01:55:15.577
to completion because this
country can build big things.

1137874765
01:55:15.578 --> 01:55:20.170
We just need competent people
at the helm to deliver them.

2456344843
01:55:20.171 --> 01:55:22.517
Prime Minister's Cameron May, Johnson,

1396973689
01:55:22.518 --> 01:55:24.866
Truss and Sunak created the worlds.

3844729493
01:55:24.866 --> 01:55:27.323
Sure, the Secretary of State did not mean

834992880
01:55:27.324 --> 01:55:28.979
to use the honourable right hon.

3459345495
01:55:28.980 --> 01:55:33.718
Member for Richmond
and Northallerton name.

3508254422
01:55:33.719 --> 01:55:34.570
Heidi Alexander.

4101014585
01:55:35.864 --> 01:55:37.668
My apologies, Madam Deputy Speaker.

1757218254
01:55:37.669 --> 01:55:41.651
Previous Prime Ministers, in my view,
created the world's most expensive

1046202932
01:55:41.652 --> 01:55:46.122
slow motion car crash
and they barely batted an eyelid.

1596451150
01:55:46.123 --> 01:55:48.078
Under this government, we've rolled up

94031098
01:55:48.079 --> 01:55:49.935
our sleeves and done the hard yards,

2569874499
01:55:49.936 --> 01:55:51.542
put in the right team in place,

3352847723
01:55:51.543 --> 01:55:54.574
and being honest about
the scale of the challenge.

2446897503
01:55:54.575 --> 01:55:57.521
Madam Deputy Speaker,
I understand that this statement

1553561352
01:55:57.522 --> 01:56:01.318
today will be met with cynicism and anger,

1851272386
01:56:01.319 --> 01:56:05.070
but I say with genuine pride
and conviction that I believe

3061989161
01:56:05.071 --> 01:56:08.370
we are finally starting to see
real delivery tunnelling.

53677536
01:56:08.865 --> 01:56:11.270
Tunnelling machines are
currently working under

3648415295
01:56:12.823 --> 01:56:15.231
Londoners feet to make
HS2 to Euston a reality.

3088941198
01:56:15.869 --> 01:56:20.018
Birmingham skyline is changing before
our eyes, with new film studios,

1719685416
01:56:20.018 --> 01:56:23.674
a sports quarter
and housing all being built

656764963
01:56:23.675 --> 01:56:27.314
around the new Curzon Street station.

2593100949
01:56:27.315 --> 01:56:29.120
This is national renewal in action.

4252935187
01:56:29.121 --> 01:56:33.671
Madam Deputy Speaker, when I last
worked with Mark wild and Mike Brown,

1026639372
01:56:33.672 --> 01:56:38.320
we took the delayed
and overbudget Crossrail project

575759548
01:56:38.321 --> 01:56:40.665
and turned it into the Elizabeth line,

2635508917
01:56:40.666 --> 01:56:43.824
which has now served more than
half a billion passengers.

3192397031
01:56:43.825 --> 01:56:44.928
We've done it before.

3040441670
01:56:44.929 --> 01:56:45.882
We'll do it again.

153816502
01:56:45.883 --> 01:56:48.040
And I commend this statement to the House.

2857564792
01:56:48.864 --> 01:56:50.467
Shadow Ministers Jerome Mayhew.

2327702334
01:56:50.468 --> 01:56:52.374
>> Thank you very much, Madam Deputy.

629567087
01:56:52.375 --> 01:56:54.281
>> Speaker, and I'm very grateful to.

3032021836
01:56:54.282 --> 01:56:58.971
>> The Secretary of State for giving
me advance sight of her statement.

1979720846
01:56:58.972 --> 01:57:01.578
The Secretary of State's
comments today demonstrate

485874691
01:57:01.579 --> 01:57:03.824
not only the challenges faced in the past,

4153167377
01:57:03.825 --> 01:57:07.523
and the reasons action was taken
to reduce the scope of HS2,

3884557310
01:57:07.524 --> 01:57:09.777
but also the significant challenges ahead

1204250918
01:57:09.777 --> 01:57:12.156
if it is finally to be delivered.

1687395521
01:57:12.157 --> 01:57:15.419
And it's true that the early
years of the HS2 project

3144770729
01:57:15.420 --> 01:57:19.172
were beset with delays and cost overruns,

1754169562
01:57:19.173 --> 01:57:23.127
with HS2 limited failing to maintain
tight control of the Budget and,

65910964
01:57:23.868 --> 01:57:27.767
frankly, Department for transport
allowing them to get away with it.

2157592266
01:57:27.768 --> 01:57:31.366
It was for this reason that
the previous government appointed

3873405384
01:57:31.368 --> 01:57:34.871
Mark wild OBE as the new chief
executive of HS2 limited,

3477603034
01:57:34.872 --> 01:57:39.620
with the clear instruction
to get a grip of

2207029878
01:57:39.621 --> 01:57:41.676
costs and robustly oversee this project.

2920620215
01:57:41.677 --> 01:57:45.830
And it's apparent from today's
statement that Hs2's leadership

1438910698
01:57:45.830 --> 01:57:48.991
under Mark wild is taking those
steps to try and achieve this.

4192301157
01:57:49.868 --> 01:57:53.029
Where there are actions that can
reduce costs in the long run,

3713841021
01:57:53.030 --> 01:57:56.303
then this side of the House
will clearly support them.

3311170907
01:57:56.304 --> 01:57:58.967
But given concerns about
trust in the project,

1906148917
01:57:58.968 --> 01:58:02.624
I hope the government and HS2
limited will set out in detail

4267889928
01:58:02.625 --> 01:58:05.422
how they believe these
measures will save money

4063091684
01:58:05.423 --> 01:58:09.476
and deliver even on this
new extended timetable.

1852331998
01:58:09.477 --> 01:58:12.836
In addition, we have to acknowledge
the deep seated infrastructure

2841694198
01:58:12.837 --> 01:58:14.893
challenges that we face in this country.

564882933
01:58:14.893 --> 01:58:16.899
When the Prime Minister was campaigning

1176373757
01:58:16.900 --> 01:58:18.768
during the last general election,

2982482760
01:58:18.770 --> 01:58:21.268
we heard a range of promises about housing

3578704369
01:58:21.268 --> 01:58:24.075
and infrastructure goals that
have completely unfounded

4116145335
01:58:24.076 --> 01:58:27.569
when they have come into
contact with reality.

2923431307
01:58:27.570 --> 01:58:29.477
That's why on this side of the House,

2444531444
01:58:29.868 --> 01:58:32.568
we propose substantial
changes to environmental

1669374955
01:58:32.569 --> 01:58:34.725
legislation to give us the freedoms needed

3109880880
01:58:34.726 --> 01:58:37.271
to cut environmental red tape,

1815689968
01:58:37.272 --> 01:58:41.873
both for business but also for
large infrastructure projects.

4030969311
01:58:41.874 --> 01:58:44.531
Even the Prime Minister does
not support regulations

2087791715
01:58:44.532 --> 01:58:48.125
that lead to a £100 million
bat tunnel, does she?

2947240980
01:58:49.871 --> 01:58:52.277
This must be addressed
because the Secretary of

611206759
01:58:52.279 --> 01:58:54.586
State has made a number
of strong statements.

2692398154
01:58:54.587 --> 01:58:56.595
And if she's angry, as she says she is,

328259263
01:58:56.596 --> 01:59:00.625
those statements must be
backed up by consequential

4110694382
01:59:00.627 --> 01:59:03.322
legislative changes that stop these cost

849112613
01:59:03.323 --> 01:59:07.121
overruns from occurring in the future.

157480173
01:59:07.122 --> 01:59:08.375
Turning to the specific.

3168825121
01:59:08.375 --> 01:59:12.570
I wish to press the Secretary of
State on matters on which those

2492819853
01:59:12.571 --> 01:59:17.184
in the sector already have indicated
that they want assurances.

2980829165
01:59:17.185 --> 01:59:19.318
For example, Madam Deputy Speaker,

3470566507
01:59:19.319 --> 01:59:22.326
what does the new project
cost figures include?

2512583390
01:59:22.327 --> 01:59:27.625
Does it include all the rolling
stock under the new plans?

2262720247
01:59:27.625 --> 01:59:30.936
To what extent is Euston funding
included in these new estimates,

3595204177
01:59:30.937 --> 01:59:32.874
and does it include signalling.

127529603
01:59:32.875 --> 01:59:36.336
Does the government intend to set
out precisely what is being funded

553990561
01:59:36.337 --> 01:59:38.326
and when the various elements will be

2854111089
01:59:38.327 --> 01:59:40.418
delivered under their new timetable?

1892992709
01:59:40.419 --> 01:59:44.127
And can the Ministers
also explain what steps

881989159
01:59:44.128 --> 01:59:46.634
the government has taken
to improve HS2 Limited's

2752098762
01:59:46.636 --> 01:59:48.892
performance when it comes
to settling claims

3071567861
01:59:48.893 --> 01:59:50.747
with those impacted by construction?

393979014
01:59:50.748 --> 01:59:54.875
Since she herself has
separately highlighted that

833132866
01:59:54.875 --> 01:59:58.476
this is an area that requires improvement.

2640069582
01:59:58.477 --> 02:00:02.326
Of course, HS2 doesn't
operate in a vacuum.

645819936
02:00:02.327 --> 02:00:06.175
On the same day that this statement
is being put before the House,

2133540505
02:00:06.176 --> 02:00:09.725
it's been announced that
the government pressure will result in 1

833309978
02:00:09.726 --> 02:00:13.281
in 7 rail services being cut on
one of Avanti West Coast routes,

1029968324
02:00:13.282 --> 02:00:17.980
following a government request
to reduce expenditure.

433425028
02:00:17.981 --> 02:00:20.530
And given the comments
made about the project,

2911887420
02:00:20.531 --> 02:00:23.382
is it appropriate that
the services on the West

3382553811
02:00:23.383 --> 02:00:27.375
Coast will offer fewer
services to passengers?

1778898026
02:00:27.375 --> 02:00:29.582
Ultimately, the government
is right to take

1165613119
02:00:29.583 --> 02:00:31.573
