2198543330
02:01:00.872 --> 02:01:02.829
and so I can only assume that perhaps,

408706909
02:01:02.830 --> 02:01:08.322
perhaps he was considering making
an apology for the dreadful

2699547755
02:01:08.323 --> 02:01:13.431
