government left this project in.

3769115198
02:01:13.432 --> 02:01:14.384
I didn't hear one.

2337426135
02:01:14.386 --> 02:01:18.637
But look, I accept the the
the manner in which he made his points.

3149701356
02:01:19.873 --> 02:01:20.826
I do also, though.

3394288732
02:01:20.827 --> 02:01:24.326
