2814881381
02:02:05.330 --> 02:02:08.830
We are in a completely
unacceptable position.

1587506108
02:02:08.830 --> 02:02:13.585
We have to acknowledge that HS2 has failed

3811865026
02:02:13.586 --> 02:02:16.774
