3790841925
02:02:16.775 --> 02:02:18.329
Madam Deputy Speaker, the hon.

365145043
02:02:18.875 --> 02:02:21.383
Gentleman asked me a number
of specific questions

3872417383
02:02:21.872 --> 02:02:23.527
and I will answer them directly.

4256515450
02:02:23.527 --> 02:02:30.381
He asks how reducing the speed to 320km/h

3730134125
02:02:30.382 --> 02:02:32.728
will save money and ensure delivery.

425747477
02:02:32.729 --> 02:02:38.230
To be clear, Madam Deputy Speaker,
this will mean that trains

1058977195
02:02:38.231 --> 02:02:42.500
