as bullet trains in Japan.

1568528637
02:02:42.502 --> 02:02:45.935
We're making three scope
changes in this announcement

1426115502
02:02:45.936 --> 02:02:48.875
today one reducing the speed,

2906866183
02:02:48.875 --> 02:02:52.325
two reducing automatic train
operation and three ensuring

3949443284
02:02:52.326 --> 02:02:57.784
that the signalling that we
put in on HS2 is aligned with

507531126
02:02:57.785 --> 02:03:02.176
the ETS system that is being rolled
