3133725602
02:03:02.177 --> 02:03:06.572
upgrade and across the Network
Rail system more broadly.

1691245352
02:03:06.573 --> 02:03:12.534
We will depend on proven technologies.

3870588207
02:03:12.535 --> 02:03:14.643
We are not taking a punt on world firsts.

4231542688
02:03:14.643 --> 02:03:17.729
I think that is the way to reduce risk

3673033514
02:03:17.730 --> 02:03:19.485
