the Planning and Infrastructure Act,

4199103298
02:03:37.531 --> 02:03:42.529
which could mean a different approach
to protected species in future.

3036809885
02:03:43.836 --> 02:03:49.774
And I gently say to him who was
overseeing this project when

687381638
02:03:49.775 --> 02:03:52.929
HS2 took the decision to
proceed with the bat tunnel,

515384957
02:03:52.930 --> 02:03:57.030
it wasn't this government,
it was his government.

930210905
02:03:57.031 --> 02:04:00.477
And we've taken actions to ensure that

1505594096
02:04:00.478 --> 02:04:03.031
regulations in future do not get in

1974524479
02:04:03.032 --> 02:04:05.489
the way of building
the homes and infrastructure

3908125498
02:04:05.875 --> 02:04:07.129
that this country needs.

1538522270
02:04:07.130 --> 02:04:11.676
He asked me specific questions
about whether the revised

3142841918
02:04:11.677 --> 02:04:14.687
cost ranges include
a number of different areas,

3636109499
02:04:14.688 --> 02:04:20.237
and I can confirm that on
Euston that there is provision

487645124
02:04:20.238 --> 02:04:22.832
within this range for
the delivery of Euston,

3192850573
02:04:22.833 --> 02:04:28.939
although we've also gone out to
market to attract private investment.

4288762914
02:04:28.940 --> 02:04:33.132
Given that in the ten year
infrastructure strategy,

2873143831
02:04:33.133 --> 02:04:36.884
we set out our ambition
to deliver the new HS2

1781100199
02:04:36.884 --> 02:04:39.526
station through a public
private partnership.

758703898
02:04:39.527 --> 02:04:39.777
The.

3028881038
02:04:39.777 --> 02:04:46.390
The signalling costs are also
included in these cost ranges.

1843212878
02:04:46.391 --> 02:04:52.077
He asked me rightly about what
action HS2 is taking to improve its

1283427910
02:04:52.078 --> 02:04:56.832
performance when it comes to settling
claims on land and property.

2480692860
02:04:56.833 --> 02:04:59.381
I know that there were very many hon.

1625863750
02:04:59.382 --> 02:05:01.437
Members in this House whose constituents

1739973093
02:05:01.438 --> 02:05:03.191
