3366908376
02:06:20.036 --> 02:06:21.791
Chair of the Select Committee, Ruth Cadbury.

1733446723
02:06:21.792 --> 02:06:23.196
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy.

3190458488
02:06:23.197 --> 02:06:28.198
