1985247435
02:06:55.735 --> 02:06:59.330
Half the project.

2052915665
02:06:59.330 --> 02:07:01.740
So we have the Aston to
Old Oak Common project.

1412265195
02:07:01.741 --> 02:07:04.482
I'm so glad that the government
picked up that and is

2179288131
02:07:04.482 --> 02:07:07.042
moving ahead on the on
the Euston element as well.

1874340637
02:07:07.043 --> 02:07:07.444
But we.

242620669
02:07:07.445 --> 02:07:12.386
Because we had the Stewart review and

832056365
02:07:12.387 --> 02:07:15.382
the the report to tell
us what went wrong to.

170381820
02:07:15.383 --> 02:07:16.286
I'm not going to.

2667933398
02:07:16.286 --> 02:07:18.938
My question is not actually going to be

548243374
02:07:18.939 --> 02:07:20.695
on HS2 because we've got the rail.

741562384
02:07:20.880 --> 02:07:24.384
Ministers and HS2 chief
exec coming to us tomorrow,

2924401455
02:07:24.386 --> 02:07:25.489
but elements that we.

2549665778
02:07:25.490 --> 02:07:30.636
That I believe are picked
up in the Lovegrove report.

