1233111337
02:08:36.433 --> 02:08:40.785
gold plating and constant
changes in policy and scope.

4000707664
02:08:40.786 --> 02:08:42.441
So she's entirely right on that.

1903921704
02:08:42.442 --> 02:08:47.089
