infrastructure in those places.

2655876647
02:09:24.395 --> 02:09:26.000
So we are learning the lessons.

2108903002
02:09:26.000 --> 02:09:28.306
>> Liberal Democrat
spokesperson Olly Glover.

562570573
02:09:28.307 --> 02:09:28.708
>> Yes.

3818290004
02:09:28.709 --> 02:09:30.866
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker And can

1939647205
02:09:30.866 --> 02:09:32.723
I start by thanking the Secretary of

2613971792
02:09:32.723 --> 02:09:34.580
State for her candour on this matter

3256401088
02:09:34.580 --> 02:09:36.488
and to the scale of the HS2 disaster,

2444780198
02:09:36.489 --> 02:09:38.596
and also for the specificity of the range

4186639880
02:09:38.597 --> 02:09:40.786
of dates that she has provided.

148381504
02:09:40.786 --> 02:09:43.646
And certainly we on these
benches agree with her intent.

2911866360
02:09:43.647 --> 02:09:46.489
We need to make the make
the most of this shambles,

45726759
02:09:46.490 --> 02:09:49.184
and it would indeed be
better to do something

3219535331
02:09:49.185 --> 02:09:51.786
