1567583222
02:09:51.786 --> 02:09:53.744
it and hope that that resets the past.

815577796
02:09:53.745 --> 02:09:56.152
It's also good news that
Secretary of State has

3441588396
02:09:56.154 --> 02:09:58.258
outlined commitment to proven technology,

295382351
02:09:58.259 --> 02:10:00.415
rather than the innovations of the future,

3386989732
02:10:00.416 --> 02:10:03.625
and warp drive and whatever else
was being talked about before,

2657124380
02:10:03.627 --> 02:10:05.182
and particularly a use of etc.

617462364
02:10:05.183 --> 02:10:07.489
s as signalling is welcome for that.

3979929869
02:10:07.490 --> 02:10:10.288
Now, Madam Deputy Speaker,
we in this country

1955258362
