And the high speed line from tours
to Bordeaux in France took 15 years,

976143999
02:10:23.538 --> 02:10:26.195
including all the planning
and all the construction.

3953126956
02:10:26.196 --> 02:10:29.103
So whilst the Secretary of
State highlighting Crossrail's

3188544328
02:10:29.104 --> 02:10:31.962
expertise on this expert panel
