And is she confident that her
expert panel has the high speed

1529681101
02:10:40.996 --> 02:10:44.053
construction and commissioning
specific skills that we need,

1495801543
02:10:44.054 --> 02:10:49.781
either from the UK or abroad,
to turn this situation around?

341891726
02:10:49.782 --> 02:10:51.388
>> And I'm grateful to the hon.

4113063642
02:10:51.880 --> 02:11:00.338
Gentleman for his support for
the overall approach that we are taking.

93436879
02:11:00.339 --> 02:11:04.886
I am reassured that both within
the executive leadership of HS2,

1184202023
02:11:04.887 --> 02:11:08.547
we have the capability
and capacity that is now needed.

76978754
02:11:08.884 --> 02:11:10.539
That wasn't the case previously.

4177951293
02:11:10.540 --> 02:11:12.844
There's a new financial director,

2626373551
02:11:12.845 --> 02:11:16.084
