179294606
02:11:57.194 --> 02:11:59.741
and then we also have the involvement of

3460377931
02:11:59.741 --> 02:12:03.086
the project representative as well.

3233090838
02:12:03.087 --> 02:12:06.286
So this is a really
significant and substantial

3555431181
02:12:06.288 --> 02:12:11.357
group of people who have all got,

342532252
02:12:11.357 --> 02:12:13.566
