seats and reliability.

4015057385
02:41:14.187 --> 02:41:16.796
And I think through this
reset we are changing that

4047534873
02:41:16.797 --> 02:41:19.406
and we are determined to
ensure, as I said earlier,

3790109672
02:41:19.407 --> 02:41:22.267
that this is the spine of
the Great British Rail network

3391098260
02:41:22.268 --> 02:41:25.227
and that we will deliver as we
renationalise the railways.

2034391608
02:41:25.228 --> 02:41:27.585
>> Tom Gordon thank you,
Madam Deputy Speaker.

464532484
02:41:27.586 --> 02:41:31.248
I thank the Secretary of State for
Secretary of State for her statement.

3750527724
02:41:31.249 --> 02:41:33.807
It's outrageous to hear
the waste and money thrown

2872814052
02:41:33.808 --> 02:41:36.062
