less funding per head

2332560868
02:41:46.098 --> 02:41:48.404
for transport than
counterparts in the South.

3767528480
02:41:48.405 --> 02:41:51.667
So does the Secretary of State
agree with me that a small amount

1180495896
02:41:51.668 --> 02:41:54.929
