3732428446
02:42:07.671 --> 02:42:10.933
I have taken the decision to reduce
the speed of HS2 to 320km/h.

959949513
02:42:10.934 --> 02:42:12.841
We believe that could save up to £2.5

466851354
02:42:12.842 --> 02:42:15.199
billion and result in
delivery a year earlier.

1208288897
02:42:15.200 --> 02:42:18.310
Given how long people have been
waiting for this new railway,

2021654960
02:42:18.311 --> 02:42:21.221
I think that's the responsible
thing to do so that people

158969817
02:42:21.222 --> 02:42:24.131
can get on these trains sooner
than they otherwise would.

2041769890
02:42:24.132 --> 02:42:26.439
I understand he's
a fierce advocate for those

2136125027
02:42:26.440 --> 02:42:28.393
rail improvements in his constituency,

3537588092
02:42:28.395 --> 02:42:30.452
and I'm sure we'll talk about those more

968665510
02:42:30.453 --> 02:42:32.209
when we get to the next transport.

657486155
02:42:32.210 --> 02:42:32.759
Questions.

3112958059
02:42:32.761 --> 02:42:35.218
>> Shockat Adam thank you,
Madam Deputy Speaker.

814701516
02:42:35.219 --> 02:42:37.828
