is that despite spending

3300451149
02:42:37.829 --> 02:42:40.235
taxpayers over £103 billion
of taxpayers money,

1933782431
02:42:40.236 --> 02:42:42.997
my son has laid more rail
track from his Lego set than

4276751018
02:42:42.998 --> 02:42:45.756
the previous government has
done from the HS2 project.

2299163070
02:42:45.757 --> 02:42:49.314
But seriously, there's considerations
and concerns from whistleblowers

3550272637
02:42:49.315 --> 02:42:52.824
who have alleged that costs were
