2103838228
02:42:55.884 --> 02:42:58.995
So before another penny spent
of the of the British taxpayer,

854842865
02:42:58.996 --> 02:43:01.604
how will the Ministers
ensure in the future they're

3560872426
02:43:01.605 --> 02:43:04.160
accountable binding mechanisms
to stop contractors

1506070303
02:43:04.161 --> 02:43:06.616
