1501414361
02:43:13.339 --> 02:43:14.341
Utmost seriousness.

961162031
02:43:14.342 --> 02:43:16.750
Can I also reassure him
when it comes to fraud,

647911574
02:43:16.752 --> 02:43:19.411
that as part of the reset
that HS2 is going through,

2018392280
02:43:19.413 --> 02:43:21.918
it is strengthening its
