944459216
02:43:23.774 --> 02:43:26.832
Because when you're spending
this amount of taxpayers money,

2254927312
02:43:26.833 --> 02:43:29.595
you should treat it as if it
was your own and the care

2492857430
02:43:29.596 --> 02:43:32.305
and attention that you would
apply to your own money.

2530638899
02:43:32.306 --> 02:43:34.463
And so we're taking all necessary steps to

4283583015
02:43:34.464 --> 02:43:36.570
make sure that we strengthen the controls

2138005545
02:43:36.571 --> 02:43:39.981
within the organisation to ensure
value for money for the taxpayer.

3908191180
02:43:39.982 --> 02:43:41.035
>> Tim Farron thank.

3587408556
02:43:41.036 --> 02:43:44.498
>> You, Madam Deputy Speaker, and
I thank the Secretary of State for

1470122820
02:43:44.499 --> 02:43:47.660
reeling out a list of very
depressing dates in the far future,

3329497025
02:43:47.661 --> 02:43:50.621
which leads more all but
the youngest of us to contemplate

795340295
02:43:50.622 --> 02:43:53.381
our mortality and what is
also what is also depressing

