3493914897
02:44:52.174 --> 02:44:53.628
>> Freddie Mierlo thank you.

583578710
02:44:53.629 --> 02:44:54.882
>> Madam Deputy Speaker.

2789044081
02:44:54.883 --> 02:44:57.190
Can I thank the Ministers
for delivering this

3057933548
02:44:57.191 --> 02:44:59.096
