I think what's really struck
me about this debate is that

1524607555
02:45:05.670 --> 02:45:09.780
the cost of HS2 is now measured
in the hundreds of billions,

769956567
02:45:09.781 --> 02:45:12.589
but what we're spending on
active travel is measured in

3249911428
02:45:12.591 --> 02:45:15.698
the hundreds of millions
the government previously committed.

1551277300
02:45:15.699 --> 02:45:18.123
I think it was only 600
million until 2030.

2593775746
02:45:18.124 --> 02:45:19.678
On active travel and projects.

793503300
02:45:19.679 --> 02:45:22.667
They're things like the time
Tottenham Greenway would

2668630616
02:45:22.668 --> 02:45:25.618
never deliver enormous
benefit to my constituents.

