travel and this project?

3000553525
02:45:33.820 --> 02:45:34.171
>> So.

3641795503
02:45:34.172 --> 02:45:36.567
>> I would gently correct him.

2547170665
02:45:36.568 --> 02:45:40.471
We may be talking about tens of
billions when it comes to HS2.

1925022039
02:45:40.472 --> 02:45:44.277
We are not talking about
hundreds of billions.

2433297057
02:45:44.277 --> 02:45:48.321
When we talk about HS2, he
makes a fair point about

230366610
02:45:48.322 --> 02:45:52.670
the importance of investment
in walking and cycling.

762052206
02:45:52.671 --> 02:45:56.323
The government is due to launch
its cycling and walking strategy,

2321691796
02:45:56.916 --> 02:45:58.270
the third iteration of it,

1083080457
02:45:58.271 --> 02:46:02.821
and we are backing that with
£600 million worth of investment

1242875028
02:46:02.822 --> 02:46:06.427
and we realise the benefits
that actually active travel,

3469229337
02:46:07.918 --> 02:46:11.911
people walking and cycling more
using public transport can have,

2128059856
02:46:11.911 --> 02:46:13.616
not just for people's own health,

1128528712
02:46:13.916 --> 02:46:17.074
it can have environmental benefits,
economic benefits as well.

4253519339
02:46:17.075 --> 02:46:20.829
And it's something that me and
the local transport Ministers care deeply

990467809
02:46:20.830 --> 02:46:25.425
about and will ensure that we
make progress on Jim Shannon.

4108722855
02:46:25.426 --> 02:46:27.231
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

2705533308
02:46:27.232 --> 02:46:29.239
Can I thank the Secretary very much for

4038893641
02:46:29.240 --> 02:46:31.471
her statement and for her positivity

1295667041
02:46:31.472 --> 02:46:36.371
and trying to make better matters
better in relation to where we are.

4243220795
02:46:36.372 --> 02:46:38.877
It talks about maximising
international standards

930579807
02:46:38.878 --> 02:46:42.562
and reshaping governance
to find efficiencies.

939071257
02:46:42.563 --> 02:46:45.120
Yet my constituents in
Northern Ireland are facing

4123059962
02:46:45.121 --> 02:46:48.824
critical infrastructure
deficits of their own.

579899547
02:46:48.825 --> 02:46:52.422
If this fundamental reset is
truly about driving economic

789493348
02:46:52.423 --> 02:46:55.231
growth and to maximise value
across the United Kingdom,

3603273728
02:46:55.916 --> 02:46:58.072
can the second step please very genuinely,

206525622
02:46:59.920 --> 02:47:03.875
explicitly outline how the billions
are clawed back from streamlining?

2988652727
02:47:03.875 --> 02:47:08.122
HS2 will be used to support
union connectivity and,

2128380124
02:47:08.123 --> 02:47:10.218
in particular, Air Passenger Duty,

3023771064
02:47:10.219 --> 02:47:12.875
which hampers connectivity
within the United Kingdom

2539502203
02:47:12.875 --> 02:47:14.830
of Great Britain and Northern Ireland.

3193696276
02:47:16.916 --> 02:47:18.170
>> Thank you, thank you.

3531662618
02:47:18.171 --> 02:47:21.170
>> I congratulate my the hon.

76540951
02:47:21.171 --> 02:47:26.120
Gentleman on leveraging
in a question on Air

2849471668
02:47:26.121 --> 02:47:28.127
Passenger Duty into a statement on HS2.

3740995705
02:47:28.128 --> 02:47:31.317
No, my hon.

3244139459
02:47:31.318 --> 02:47:32.170
Friend is right.

1118894968
02:47:32.171 --> 02:47:35.699
He never misses an opportunity.

3622832250
02:47:35.700 --> 02:47:40.782
You know, I, I am obviously very
concerned to ensure that connectivity

3756775986
02:47:40.783 --> 02:47:45.985
between the mainland UK
and Northern Ireland remains,

2990154808
02:47:45.986 --> 02:47:50.075
that it's reliable, that
it's affordable for people,

535019605
02:47:50.076 --> 02:47:54.284
and I will be sure to talk
to him further about what

2028606085
02:47:54.920 --> 02:47:57.428
more could be done aside
from Air Passenger Duty,

3659239734
02:47:57.921 --> 02:47:59.727
which is a matter for the Treasury.

1937366062
02:47:59.728 --> 02:48:02.186
If there's anything that
my department can do to

2329144043
02:48:02.187 --> 02:48:04.392
improve the situation
for his constituents,

604452455
02:48:04.393 --> 02:48:06.723
I'd be only too happy to talk to him.

3187060194
02:48:06.725 --> 02:48:10.625
Can I thank the Secretary of State
for her statement this afternoon?

588250141
02:48:10.625 --> 02:48:14.588
I will allow a couple of moments
for the front bench to swap over.

2482600786
02:48:28.454 --> 02:48:31.204
The clerk will now proceed
to read The clerk will

2863918665
02:48:31.205 --> 02:48:33.363
