3218269389
02:49:02.927 --> 02:49:05.370
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

4083511004
02:49:05.371 --> 02:49:08.576
I beg to move the amendment
as on the Order Paper.

31154076
02:49:08.577 --> 02:49:12.566
And in fact, this may be our last
meeting across this Dispatch Box

963092817
02:49:12.567 --> 02:49:16.830
because the Secretary of State
is once again on manoeuvres.

2721820251
02:49:16.832 --> 02:49:20.029
So considering he's
gunning for a promotion,

2876631753
02:49:20.030 --> 02:49:23.379
let's review his record, shall we?

1917314569
02:49:23.380 --> 02:49:25.627
He promised in the election that he would

1872586627
02:49:25.628 --> 02:49:29.228
cut everybody's energy bills by £300.

82995780
02:49:29.229 --> 02:49:30.482
And what's he delivered?

1277917726
02:49:30.482 --> 02:49:34.375
Energy bills up by £200
thanks to his plans.

3607913400
02:49:34.377 --> 02:49:36.928
He said he would protect pensioners.

778781563
02:49:36.929 --> 02:49:40.428
But weeks into office he acts
the Winter Fuel Payment,

3225047773
02:49:40.429 --> 02:49:42.833
a policy that many of them have cited as

1868524137
02:49:42.834 --> 02:49:45.421
their worst political decision in power.

1884259262
02:49:45.422 --> 02:49:50.027
He promised that Great British
energy would lead to,

2020642865
02:49:50.027 --> 02:49:52.922
and I quote, a mind blowing
reduction in bills.

2980446752
02:49:52.923 --> 02:49:57.683
And yet, two years in, it hasn't
taken a penny off household bills.

2945715792
02:49:57.684 --> 02:50:01.881
But it has given a six figure
salary to one of his mates.

865725356
02:50:01.882 --> 02:50:06.625
And now we learn that Great British
Energy has been putting solar

3241263854
02:50:06.625 --> 02:50:09.835
panels made by Chinese slave
labour on British primary schools,

900193426
02:50:09.836 --> 02:50:14.288
something he promised this
House he would not do.

1688750280
02:50:14.289 --> 02:50:15.091
So what's next?

699915690
02:50:15.092 --> 02:50:19.220
Oh, that's right, he said he
could control the price of wind.

3623661636
02:50:19.221 --> 02:50:21.177
But his botched wind auction signed us

1831879968
02:50:21.178 --> 02:50:23.680
up to the highest prices in a decade,

3454610969
02:50:23.681 --> 02:50:28.879
way more than the cost of
electricity that he inherited.

761485368
02:50:30.924 --> 02:50:33.430
Promise after broken
promise, bills up pensioners

1577751157
02:50:34.924 --> 02:50:36.377
betrayed six figure salaries

393852219
02:50:36.378 --> 02:50:39.928
for his mates and eye watering
contracts for wind developers.

480555846
02:50:39.929 --> 02:50:45.288
And now, to top it all off,
a so-called energy independence

576121675
02:50:45.928 --> 02:50:48.035
bill which would shut down the North Sea.

3275515144
02:50:48.036 --> 02:50:52.631
The greatest act of industrial
self-harm in a generation.

2405249194
02:50:53.924 --> 02:50:59.430
If that gets you a promotion in
the Labour Party, then Lord help us all.

1843098107
02:50:59.431 --> 02:51:03.676
So let's turn to this
so-called Energy Independence

1183363994
02:51:03.677 --> 02:51:06.975
Bill for true energy independence.

1127659009
02:51:06.976 --> 02:51:08.432
We need our own oil and gas.

345187085
02:51:08.433 --> 02:51:13.441
But this bill enforces the wilful
destruction of the North Sea.

416648853
02:51:13.442 --> 02:51:16.102
We need our own petrol,
diesel and will in a moment.

2519048753
02:51:16.103 --> 02:51:18.625
We need our own petrol,
diesel and jet fuel.

559607291
02:51:18.627 --> 02:51:22.726
But this bill does nothing
to save our refineries,

1789992465
02:51:22.727 --> 02:51:24.582
which are being taxed into oblivion.

1659267002
02:51:24.583 --> 02:51:27.469
We need an electricity system
which keeps the lights

243765053
02:51:27.470 --> 02:51:29.475
on for British households and industry.

3637626299
02:51:29.476 --> 02:51:33.378
But his plan will leave us at
the mercy of foreign imports.

1871149552
02:51:33.379 --> 02:51:34.631
This isn't independence.

1859337673
02:51:34.632 --> 02:51:36.525
It doesn't even come close.

502694830
02:51:36.526 --> 02:51:40.079
It's an energy dependence bill
that would leave us weaker,

2855202228
02:51:40.080 --> 02:51:43.734
poorer and more reliant
on foreign regimes.

2738125343
02:51:43.735 --> 02:51:46.178
>> Grateful to her for giving way.

574322626
02:51:46.179 --> 02:51:48.134
She says that for energy independence,

3575399675
02:51:48.134 --> 02:51:53.038
we need our own oil and gas rather
than investing in renewables.

2923043975
02:51:53.039 --> 02:51:57.129
She'll know that under her government,
the government paid £44 billion

2839350098
02:51:57.130 --> 02:52:01.482
