the time of the Ukraine price spike.

1732217730
02:52:01.482 --> 02:52:06.078
Can she tell us how much were our
bills reduced as a result of

3204484061
02:52:06.079 --> 02:52:09.377
having our own oil and gas when
the Ukraine crisis happened?

3929560747
02:52:09.378 --> 02:52:11.711
>> Firstly, let me say to the hon.

2764531900
02:52:11.712 --> 02:52:13.768
Gentleman bills came down £500 under me.

3286084404
02:52:13.768 --> 02:52:17.530
They've gone up £200 because of
the Secretary of State's plans.

393411255
02:52:17.531 --> 02:52:20.285
And let me tell him another
hard truth cutting

3059643096
02:52:20.286 --> 02:52:24.475
off production in the North Sea.

602187414
02:52:24.476 --> 02:52:26.180
He should listen learn something.

1202513267
02:52:26.181 --> 02:52:30.237
Cutting off production in
the North Sea use any less.

3725996027
02:52:30.238 --> 02:52:33.389
Oil and gas production is
not linked to consumption.

1999576939
02:52:34.934 --> 02:52:39.035
All that it means is that we'll
import more of that gas from abroad.

3307533960
02:52:39.036 --> 02:52:39.838
That is weaker.

246298029
02:52:39.839 --> 02:52:43.286
That makes us more reliant on imports.

2064834641
02:52:43.286 --> 02:52:44.642
Now he used up his chance.

178550287
02:52:44.643 --> 02:52:46.649
He should have asked a better question.

490434993
02:52:46.650 --> 02:52:52.378
Now, look, there are some parts
of this work that I welcome.

2697789504
02:52:52.379 --> 02:52:54.183
The Fingleton review is impressive.

764904069
02:52:54.184 --> 02:52:55.387
I thank those involved.

362507779
02:52:55.388 --> 02:52:59.000
And as I've made clear before, we
will support this work going forward.

3424636079
02:52:59.000 --> 02:53:02.463
Nuclear is the only form of energy
that can provide round the clock,

3151746803
02:53:02.464 --> 02:53:03.516
totally clean power,

1526538787
02:53:03.517 --> 02:53:05.472
and I'll always support policies which

2444457705
02:53:05.473 --> 02:53:08.884
make it as easy as possible to build.

3753034683
02:53:08.884 --> 02:53:10.239
However, there is a catch.

1293586393
02:53:10.240 --> 02:53:13.550
The Secretary of State says he
wants to ease nuclear regulations,

1759849020
02:53:13.551 --> 02:53:16.428
whilst at the very same
time he's cancelled

2118230298
02:53:16.429 --> 02:53:18.486
