4268608297
02:53:18.928 --> 02:53:21.134
by cancelling the third
large scale nuclear

2626640279
02:53:21.134 --> 02:53:23.286
power station that I signed off.

1218875386
02:53:23.286 --> 02:53:27.829
He has killed the nuclear pipeline.

1415077317
02:53:27.830 --> 02:53:29.535
He is repeating his own mistakes.

1695767357
02:53:29.536 --> 02:53:32.285
We are set to have yet
another Labour government,

2699124348
02:53:33.931 --> 02:53:36.238
which has failed to start
a singular nuclear,

3078403911
02:53:36.239 --> 02:53:39.582
new, large scale nuclear power plant.

3571918080
02:53:39.583 --> 02:53:44.296
And now we hear Natural England
are adding yet more delays

1313470542
02:53:44.297 --> 02:53:47.284
