nationally say they want fracking.

1663702672
03:26:56.980 --> 03:26:59.285
And then their representatives
in Scarborough

3322049587
03:26:59.286 --> 03:27:01.643
and Lancashire seem to
say they're against it.

10842328
03:27:01.644 --> 03:27:04.805
And we're going to be asking from
now to the general election,

1246480610
03:27:04.806 --> 03:27:07.713
where reform candidates stand
with the fracking industry.

2243729035
03:27:07.714 --> 03:27:07.914
No.

2507850226
03:27:07.915 --> 03:27:10.072
So this is the approach to energy security

1331023057
03:27:10.073 --> 03:27:11.927
that underpins this Gracious Speech.

483070062
03:27:11.928 --> 03:27:13.935
Above all, we will learn the lessons of

2324551293
03:27:13.936 --> 03:27:15.692
the fossil fuel crisis of our age.

2056599912
03:27:15.693 --> 03:27:19.302
We will build our energy independence,
tackle the affordability crisis,

1283989841
03:27:19.303 --> 03:27:21.960
deliver good jobs
and investment in our communities,

768131064
03:27:21.961 --> 03:27:23.465
and make the right decisions.

2201947481
03:27:23.466 --> 03:27:26.373
Madam Deputy Speaker, for
today's and future generations,

1258827898
03:27:26.374 --> 03:27:28.782
and I commend the Gracious
Speech to the House.

4284885988
03:27:28.783 --> 03:27:30.940
>> Before I call the Lib Dem spokesperson,

4277270485
03:27:30.941 --> 03:27:32.998
I think it would be helpful to everybody

3152905763
03:27:32.999 --> 03:27:35.006
to know there will be an immediate five

3798932611
03:27:35.007 --> 03:27:37.013
minute time limit after she has spoken.

3437358954
03:27:37.014 --> 03:27:40.065
>> Pippa Heylings thank
you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

610034167
03:27:40.066 --> 03:27:41.568
>> And oil and gas.

1591995489
03:27:41.569 --> 03:27:42.572
Prices have a long.

374963310
03:27:42.573 --> 03:27:44.980
>> History of spiking
and damaging our economy.

2916424807
03:27:44.981 --> 03:27:46.035
>> The UK was among.

2185776787
03:27:46.036 --> 03:27:47.842
>> The worst hit in Western Europe.

4203481864
03:27:47.843 --> 03:27:51.367
>> By the price shock
following Russia's invasion.

2241849303
03:27:51.368 --> 03:27:52.414
Of Ukraine.

915732193
03:27:52.415 --> 03:27:53.017
>> In 2022.

937705151
03:27:53.018 --> 03:27:55.807
>> So as long as we
remain tied to volatile

961835215
03:27:55.808 --> 03:27:58.413
international fossil fuel markets,

1852116426
03:27:58.414 --> 03:28:01.968
then dictators and foreign wars
will have a grip on our economy

2414759088
03:28:01.969 --> 03:28:06.215
and on the pockets of families
and pensioners across this country.

3314945034
03:28:06.216 --> 03:28:09.872
So surely it is time to
wake up to that reality

1624357400
03:28:09.873 --> 03:28:11.629
and learn the lessons of the past.

608821738
03:28:11.630 --> 03:28:15.128
And that is why we Liberal Democrats
do welcome the government

1864889762
03:28:15.961 --> 03:28:18.367
bringing forward a bill
on energy independence.

955874369
03:28:18.368 --> 03:28:20.474
We will scrutinise it carefully to ensure

2824014675
03:28:20.475 --> 03:28:22.430
that the urgent and ambitious measures

4040950242
03:28:22.431 --> 03:28:24.712
necessary for the energy transition are

1524841289
03:28:24.713 --> 03:28:26.417
there bringing down energy bills,

3447553772
03:28:26.960 --> 03:28:29.066
ensuring energy security but also a fair,

4150760164
03:28:31.960 --> 03:28:34.516
managed and prosperous
transition to clean energy.

4235046018
03:28:35.960 --> 03:28:38.566
Madam Deputy Speaker, as
households nervously await

3058633896
03:28:38.965 --> 03:28:41.573
the announcement of
the energy price cap next week,

3177216244
03:28:41.920 --> 03:28:44.276
with forecasts showing
households could be hit

836660001
03:28:46.961 --> 03:28:49.119
with a £300 Trump war tax on energy bills.

2553090081
03:28:49.120 --> 03:28:53.566
We Liberal Democrats are clear
that the best way to get down

2758938120
03:28:53.567 --> 03:28:58.811
energy bills is through
home grown renewable power.

2441336703
03:28:58.812 --> 03:29:00.015
With prices we control.

1934673521
03:29:00.016 --> 03:29:00.869
I will give way.

3854276616
03:29:00.870 --> 03:29:02.224
>> I thank the honourable.

1691140758
03:29:02.225 --> 03:29:03.429
>> Lady for giving way.

273628562
03:29:03.430 --> 03:29:05.790
I know the Lib Dems are
a big fan of localism.

881609687
03:29:05.791 --> 03:29:08.752
This isn't a dig by the way,
in my Chris Hinchliff Harlow,

483581968
03:29:08.753 --> 03:29:10.508
we've got a primary school church,

1793911119
03:29:10.509 --> 03:29:12.967
Langley Primary School
that has led the way when

2791863479
03:29:12.968 --> 03:29:14.975
it comes to solar panels on their roof,

3930443238
03:29:14.976 --> 03:29:17.082
and they're actually able to generate all

1149979439
03:29:17.083 --> 03:29:19.390
the energy they need
from those solar panels.

2317994760
03:29:19.391 --> 03:29:22.953
So would she welcome the work that
this government are doing to ensure

1212443672
03:29:22.954 --> 03:29:26.014
that other schools can benefit
from the same sort of system?

51669163
03:29:26.015 --> 03:29:26.466
>> Yeah.

3727298462
03:29:26.467 --> 03:29:27.971
>> I definitely welcome that.

444701846
03:29:27.972 --> 03:29:31.487
And as you will see in my speech,
we want to go even further on that.

4198782718
03:29:31.488 --> 03:29:33.947
And as we know, it is
liberal Democrats that fix

836564214
03:29:33.948 --> 03:29:36.314
people's roofs and put
solar panels on there.

2109061592
03:29:36.315 --> 03:29:37.068
So we will do.

697744113
03:29:37.069 --> 03:29:40.373
But for too long, the pace
of change has been too slow,

2035301100
03:29:40.374 --> 03:29:43.926
and it's left people
and businesses trapped

842857563
03:29:43.927 --> 03:29:46.820
and at the mercy of
a broken energy system,

3510135972
03:29:46.821 --> 03:29:49.127
which they're literally
paying the price for.

4268609632
03:29:49.128 --> 03:29:51.938
So it's time to take back
control of our energy future.

3903569661
03:29:51.939 --> 03:29:54.870
And that does start with our communities.

1392778870
03:29:54.871 --> 03:29:58.514
And in the last session of
Parliament, I welcome the government

1221738242
03:29:58.515 --> 03:30:00.821
agreeing with our calls
to include community,

3328645180
03:30:01.964 --> 03:30:05.216
energy and community benefits
in the GB Energy Act.

906510571
03:30:05.217 --> 03:30:06.922
But now communities must be given

1021935480
03:30:06.923 --> 03:30:11.573
the right to sell and buy energy locally,

302792028
03:30:11.574 --> 03:30:14.875
and we must mandate community
benefit requirements

2407521894
03:30:14.876 --> 03:30:17.330
where communities host
renewable infrastructure.

4197739570
03:30:17.331 --> 03:30:20.578
The transition that is done
with them, not to them.

2362471779
03:30:20.579 --> 03:30:23.288
And I also welcome
the adoption of the sunshine Bill,

728410215
03:30:23.289 --> 03:30:24.392
introduced by my hon.

2323334162
03:30:24.393 --> 03:30:26.147
Friend, the Member for Cheltenham,

1094269670
03:30:26.968 --> 03:30:29.024
requiring solar panels on all new homes.

2688747716
03:30:29.025 --> 03:30:32.720
But why wait until 2027
and why not go further?

567851717
03:30:32.721 --> 03:30:35.519
We Liberal Democrats want to see solar on

428232946
03:30:35.520 --> 03:30:37.828
new warehouses and car parks turning

3545790711
03:30:37.829 --> 03:30:41.288
rooftops across the country into
sources of clean, affordable power.

3804012031
03:30:41.289 --> 03:30:45.485
And we also want to see solar
panels on schools and hospitals.

248303343
03:30:46.964 --> 03:30:50.916
Since 2019, energy bills for schools
and the NHS have more than doubled,

907585659
03:30:50.917 --> 03:30:52.319
forcing impossible choices.

843390707
03:30:53.968 --> 03:30:57.870
Choices between heating and healthcare
or between bills over books.

2175018101
03:30:57.871 --> 03:31:02.170
So the current government investment
reaches less than 1% of schools.

3926467997
03:31:02.171 --> 03:31:04.923
So Liberal Democrats would
go further and faster,

4057714021
03:31:04.924 --> 03:31:09.514
helping protect frontline budgets
for our schools and hospitals.

1334163039
03:31:09.515 --> 03:31:11.672
Families, too, want to do the right thing,

516780088
03:31:11.673 --> 03:31:14.634
and there has been a record
increase in the sales of solar

3100243753
03:31:14.635 --> 03:31:17.546
panels and heat pumps since
the start of the war in Iran.

2607580490
03:31:17.547 --> 03:31:21.007
We must build on this momentum, help
households and small businesses

1979176431
03:31:21.008 --> 03:31:23.867
take back control of their
bills, giving access, we say,

2193748312
03:31:23.868 --> 03:31:27.769
to zero or low interest loans for
upgrading properties by establishing

4014013922
03:31:27.770 --> 03:31:31.216
an energy security bank to
support electrification.

2252953082
03:31:31.217 --> 03:31:35.025
However, at the same time, we do need
to fix the broken energy market.

989717271
03:31:35.026 --> 03:31:38.019
It remains absurd that
electricity is still

3193281641
03:31:38.020 --> 03:31:40.418
priced so highly compared with gas,

4047337363
03:31:40.419 --> 03:31:43.682
and that means that people
are often not rewarded

3500479693
03:31:43.683 --> 03:31:46.371
for electrifying their
homes and businesses.

2578459541
03:31:46.372 --> 03:31:48.919
And it's also crazy that consumers are

1978529044
03:31:48.920 --> 03:31:50.876
paying billions to switch off our wind

3929887521
03:31:50.877 --> 03:31:54.466
turbines when the grid cannot cope
with surplus renewable generation.

104652448
03:31:54.467 --> 03:31:57.378
And that is why I welcome
the recent steps taken to begin

4064408199
03:31:57.379 --> 03:32:01.019
breaking the link between
gas and electricity prices,

200274693
03:32:01.020 --> 03:32:03.578
a reform long called for
by the Liberal Democrats.

3772512088
03:32:03.579 --> 03:32:06.690
But we urge government to go
further and faster in this bill.

1280248578
03:32:06.691 --> 03:32:09.318
Moving unfair policy levies
off electricity bills,

2848333460
03:32:09.319 --> 03:32:12.779
providing a progressive social
energy tariff for those

3830435483
03:32:12.780 --> 03:32:16.625
unable to absorb these
repeated bill shocks,

3581145934
03:32:16.626 --> 03:32:20.166
upgrading the infrastructure
and ensuring that customers directly

2024629229
03:32:20.167 --> 03:32:23.073
benefit from cheaper renewable
power through flexibility.

1013456187
03:32:23.074 --> 03:32:26.069
When the surplus renewable generation.

183731592
03:32:26.070 --> 03:32:31.325
Yes, we need energy independence,
but that doesn't mean isolation.

1019646061
03:32:31.326 --> 03:32:36.765
So the UK and the EU have deeply
interconnected energy systems.

249019760
03:32:36.766 --> 03:32:40.678
But the damaging Brexit deal has meant
a huge increase in energy costs.

3517479506
03:32:40.679 --> 03:32:43.529
Our future lies ever closer in ever closer

1150680125
03:32:43.530 --> 03:32:46.170
energy ties to our nearest neighbours,

794428305
03:32:46.171 --> 03:32:50.921
and this government needs to
drop its red lines on Europe,

797359729
03:32:50.922 --> 03:32:55.467
rejoining the EU internal electricity
market and linking our emissions

2674945849
03:32:55.468 --> 03:33:00.119
trading schemes will reduce costs
and strengthen resilience.

3068169375
03:33:00.120 --> 03:33:02.519
Madam Deputy Speaker, my right hon.

4074796366
03:33:02.520 --> 03:33:06.469
Friend the Member for Kingston
and Surbiton was right

2378273920
03:33:06.470 --> 03:33:09.029
to say that it is fantasy
and fabrication for some

1581540036
03:33:09.030 --> 03:33:11.626
in this House to pretend
that there is a solution

2356674817
03:33:11.627 --> 03:33:14.675
in the North Sea to
people's high energy bills.

3836012106
03:33:14.676 --> 03:33:18.624
Even when North Sea production was
at its peak nearly 30 years ago,

707292498
03:33:18.625 --> 03:33:21.083
the UK was still exposed
to global price shocks.

2780681257
03:33:21.084 --> 03:33:25.172
Because we have been price takers.

187031514
03:33:25.173 --> 03:33:28.572
Nor is the answer fracking, as
some are calling for destroying

3675507215
03:33:28.573 --> 03:33:33.022
our countryside
and polluting our waterways.

3322497152
03:33:33.023 --> 03:33:35.774
We will push for a complete
ban on fracking and have

995042715
03:33:35.775 --> 03:33:41.024
complete clarity on closing
all of the loopholes.

90290276
03:33:41.025 --> 03:33:43.983
We do need a secure energy
mix that includes nuclear,

3203242414
03:33:43.984 --> 03:33:46.522
and we do believe that small nuclear,

1454025765
03:33:46.523 --> 03:33:50.177
small modular reactors have
great potential to strengthen

3862382885
03:33:50.178 --> 03:33:55.521
energy security alongside renewables,

3719517669
03:33:55.522 --> 03:33:59.381
oil and gas will also be part of
that energy mix for decades to come.

866507127
03:33:59.969 --> 03:34:04.320
But we must recognise the need for
a fair and managed energy transition,

1498461572
03:34:04.321 --> 03:34:08.222
given that our remaining
reserves are in decline,

2235498119
03:34:08.223 --> 03:34:10.368
communities cannot be left behind.

1785581531
03:34:10.369 --> 03:34:15.326
So we urge the government to establish
a Just Transition Commission,

1134865808
03:34:15.327 --> 03:34:17.433
future proof supply chain jobs and enable

1864581047
03:34:17.434 --> 03:34:19.520
the retention of our brilliant,

885575998
03:34:19.521 --> 03:34:21.828
skilled oil and gas
workers into high quality

4181177883
03:34:21.829 --> 03:34:23.734
jobs in renewables and other sectors.

1407187395
03:34:23.735 --> 03:34:25.473
I will give way.

2488589382
03:34:25.474 --> 03:34:26.176
>> Thank you.

128014421
03:34:26.177 --> 03:34:26.879
Does the hon.

771868112
03:34:26.880 --> 03:34:29.489
Lady agree that new licences
in the North Sea would

3859996855
03:34:29.490 --> 03:34:32.176
help protect the workforce
and the supply chain,

4233193604
03:34:32.177 --> 03:34:37.225
in order to help with
the transition to new energies?

476458357
03:34:37.226 --> 03:34:41.225
>> I think research has
shown that the hundreds

1365888706
03:34:41.226 --> 03:34:46.731
of new oil and gas licences awarded by

3383274939
03:34:46.732 --> 03:34:49.728
the government between
2010 and 2024 has resulted

2042613432
03:34:49.729 --> 03:34:52.071
in just about 36 days of extra gas.

182926128
03:34:52.072 --> 03:34:55.625
What we need to look at are
the jobs that can move into.

1827799819
03:34:55.626 --> 03:34:59.925
I think there are 75,000
jobs that were lost without

2547142618
03:34:59.926 --> 03:35:02.483
any cries and outcries from
the government before.

2980905746
03:35:02.484 --> 03:35:05.376
We are looking at a just
energy transition that really

829403218
03:35:05.377 --> 03:35:08.324
does help those high skilled
workers into business.

839917130
03:35:08.972 --> 03:35:10.828
On that point, I'll just keep going.

763475364
03:35:10.829 --> 03:35:17.622
Madam Deputy Speaker, what
proponents of prolonged overreliance

4223515302
03:35:17.623 --> 03:35:21.468
on fossil fuels often ignore
is the cost of inaction.

755746928
03:35:21.469 --> 03:35:25.927
There is overwhelming scientific
consensus that transitioning away from

2109985536
03:35:25.928 --> 03:35:29.338
fossil fuels is essential for our
efforts to tackle climate change.

3392190151
03:35:29.339 --> 03:35:31.895
Communities around
the country are already feeling

2856214771
03:35:31.896 --> 03:35:34.369
the impacts and costs of
extreme weather events.

1926423454
03:35:34.370 --> 03:35:36.726
My constituency of South
Cambridgeshire is one

164998353
03:35:36.727 --> 03:35:38.884
of the most water stressed in the country,

951324568
03:35:41.928 --> 03:35:45.874
and last month we saw 5% of annual
rainfall and we're feeling it.

1260825073
03:35:45.875 --> 03:35:48.983
Floods and droughts have battered
farmers across the country.

4066001275
03:35:48.984 --> 03:35:52.646
They're reeling from the worst harvest
on record, and that will lead to,

491546524
03:35:52.976 --> 03:35:58.423
you know, problems with food security
and will put up our food prices.

4179639863
03:35:58.424 --> 03:36:02.883
And one avoidable death is
one too many for the elderly

3260668525
03:36:02.884 --> 03:36:07.425
and vulnerable during
recurrent heat waves.

2564229379
03:36:07.426 --> 03:36:10.726
Nor does anyone want ravaging
wildfires ripping through

562928959
03:36:10.727 --> 03:36:14.934
our most treasured woodlands
and national parks.

77260789
03:36:14.935 --> 03:36:19.677
As the government suppressed
national security assessment on

3628016601
03:36:19.972 --> 03:36:23.268
global biodiversity loss
and ecosystem collapse laid bare,

2056422990
03:36:23.269 --> 03:36:26.577
the destruction of nature
threatens the UK's resilience,

1837474643
03:36:26.578 --> 03:36:28.281
prosperity and national security.

1737211941
03:36:28.972 --> 03:36:30.527
People want to know the truth.

2640769982
03:36:30.528 --> 03:36:33.887
In my constituency of South
Cambridgeshire and across the country,

2510574626
03:36:33.971 --> 03:36:36.175
people's emergency
briefings are happening.

1702162449
03:36:36.176 --> 03:36:37.529
People are taking control.

3810400017
03:36:37.530 --> 03:36:42.779
They want to know and be better prepared.

3073988913
03:36:42.780 --> 03:36:45.369
And that's why we must
also look to prepare

638397732
03:36:45.370 --> 03:36:47.326
for the climate shocks we can't avoid,

331452673
03:36:49.976 --> 03:36:52.383
and that's why we reject
the government's false

870016338
03:36:53.972 --> 03:36:55.876
dichotomy between climate and nature,

1180759044
03:36:55.877 --> 03:36:59.527
saying that nature is a blocker to growth.

1476117182
03:36:59.528 --> 03:37:01.473
We have to be better prepared.

3200502793
03:37:01.474 --> 03:37:04.784
We have to overcome the silos
between energy, climate and nature.

644367329
03:37:04.785 --> 03:37:07.580
We need to promote nature
based approaches to both

2775362978
03:37:07.581 --> 03:37:10.376
capture carbon as well as
to adapt, storing water,

3947481884
03:37:10.377 --> 03:37:13.883
regenerating our soil, cooling
buildings and protecting

2785351792
03:37:13.884 --> 03:37:16.472
people's homes from being uninsurable.

1891318626
03:37:16.473 --> 03:37:19.176
Madam Deputy Speaker,
a secure future for our

1485429406
03:37:19.177 --> 03:37:23.026
country depends on our
energy independence,

1826501583
03:37:23.027 --> 03:37:27.078
restored nature and resilient communities

1501004443
03:37:27.079 --> 03:37:28.783
meeting our responsibility to our

1890728761
03:37:28.784 --> 03:37:30.890
children and young people for a healthier

1328403650
03:37:30.891 --> 03:37:32.495
future for generations to come.

3411757886
03:37:32.496 --> 03:37:33.599
Thank you, thank you.

3387892409
03:37:33.600 --> 03:37:36.057
>> Chair of the Select
Committee, Bill Esterson.

3659468614
03:37:36.058 --> 03:37:38.365
>> Thank you very much,
Madam Deputy Speaker.

688479662
03:37:38.366 --> 03:37:40.622
Will the Select Committee
has taken evidence

3180456098
03:37:40.623 --> 03:37:44.942
on much of what is in the gracious speech,

3668814207
03:37:44.943 --> 03:37:49.724
and a big part of the debate today
has been about the threat that we

140804429
03:37:49.725 --> 03:37:54.877
face as a result of the second fossil
fuel crisis within five years.

278038144
03:37:54.878 --> 03:37:58.831
I remember the first 1 in 1973.

4213086179
03:37:58.832 --> 03:38:01.775
Candles on the table was
fun as a six year old.

1718876322
03:38:01.776 --> 03:38:04.424
Not much fun for most of the country.

368167247
03:38:04.425 --> 03:38:09.330
And we've repeated that experience
multiple times ever since.

1049182910
03:38:09.331 --> 03:38:12.133
But in order to address
the challenge of the fossil

1947655076
