in Westmorland and indeed across
the whole of our country.

3488299973
04:22:47.731 --> 04:22:51.074
But so far we have yet to run out.

2066963411
04:22:51.075 --> 04:22:53.983
But the International Energy
Agency warned just last week

2926333900
04:22:53.984 --> 04:22:57.476
that oil inventories are being
depleted at a record pace.

2715816219
04:22:57.477 --> 04:23:01.369
Governments, companies and consumers
need therefore to be ready.

741732120
04:23:01.370 --> 04:23:01.771
Are we?

1752362822
04:23:01.772 --> 04:23:02.726
I do not think so.

248545939
04:23:02.727 --> 04:23:05.773
Energy security is now
utterly and totally urgent.

2229487597
04:23:05.775 --> 04:23:08.629
If I cannot convince
you of all the science

2372595350
04:23:08.630 --> 04:23:10.736
that points to human made climate change,

2104342353
04:23:10.737 --> 04:23:13.847
the need to tackle it, that
catastrophic blight that we face.

3952006518
04:23:13.848 --> 04:23:17.679
If I cannot convince you on that
level, surely I must be able to

679673375
04:23:17.680 --> 04:23:20.939
convince you that our energy
security rests on renewable energy,

3600810295
04:23:20.940 --> 04:23:24.574
domestically produced, because
Putin cannot turn off the sun,

135286627
04:23:24.575 --> 04:23:27.523
the wind, or our waves,
surely we should be therefore

4178759886
04:23:27.525 --> 04:23:29.378
rejoining the European international

4122481044
04:23:29.379 --> 04:23:31.675
energy market and we should be investing

462145888
04:23:31.676 --> 04:23:33.531
massively in the national grid grid.

1913800689
04:23:33.532 --> 04:23:34.585
But it's also vital.

1213404315
04:23:34.586 --> 04:23:35.840
We recognise, as my hon.

827197841
04:23:36.020 --> 04:23:37.674
Friend, rightly and wisely said,

606073567
04:23:37.675 --> 04:23:39.932
the importance of food
security in all this.

1577164336
04:23:39.933 --> 04:23:44.585
The United Kingdom is currently
only 55% food secure.

3943539243
04:23:44.586 --> 04:23:45.236
Outsourcing.

136528138
04:23:45.237 --> 04:23:48.772
The outsourcing of our agriculture has

1403355161
04:23:48.773 --> 04:23:51.471
become a national security liability.

721220544
04:23:51.472 --> 04:23:54.731
We need more short, diversified
food chains with more incentives

1165319212
04:23:54.732 --> 04:23:57.273
to primary producers to
grow food domestically.

4283262787
04:23:57.275 --> 04:23:59.779
The problem is, though,
the England England is

2987089873
04:23:59.780 --> 04:24:01.937
now the only country in the United Kingdom

3950718328
04:24:01.938 --> 04:24:04.697
and the only country in Europe
that no longer provides

1627841325
04:24:04.698 --> 04:24:07.675
support for our farmers to produce food.

1201952889
04:24:07.676 --> 04:24:09.933
Now, maybe we could agree
that back in 2020,

52038122
04:24:09.934 --> 04:24:13.043
when the Environmental Land
Management Scheme was being drawn

3990161644
04:24:13.044 --> 04:24:16.153
up by the previous government
and adopted by this government,

3741708273
04:24:16.154 --> 04:24:19.923
maybe we could agree that that
was how things felt at the time.

1896877759
04:24:19.924 --> 04:24:21.328
But the facts have changed.

3121565493
04:24:22.023 --> 04:24:24.283
It's time to change our
mind and to back our

2312687070
04:24:24.284 --> 04:24:26.391
farmers to produce the food that we need.

309447597
04:24:26.392 --> 04:24:28.722
The facts have changed.

3651024141
04:24:28.723 --> 04:24:32.378
Food producers food prices are
projected to be 50% higher

3641559551
04:24:32.379 --> 04:24:35.973
in November this year
than they were in 2021.

1669483798
04:24:35.974 --> 04:24:39.271
Agricultural inflation is
double regular inflation

458921130
04:24:39.272 --> 04:24:41.176
and therefore feeding food inflation,

2075607580
04:24:41.177 --> 04:24:43.630
which will follow
and harm our communities.

3400677854
04:24:43.632 --> 04:24:47.271
And of course, we live against
the backdrop of uncertainty,

1245499284
04:24:47.272 --> 04:24:49.376
the technological and geopolitical shifts

1107513411
04:24:49.377 --> 04:24:51.182
that we are living through include,

373118671
04:24:51.183 --> 04:24:53.692
of course, the very threat
to the future of NATO,

1435558140
04:24:54.020 --> 04:24:55.974
Russian and China, Chinese aggression.

750858622
04:24:55.975 --> 04:24:58.923
So our energy, food
and military resistance,

2796471718
04:24:58.924 --> 04:25:03.126
resilience matters more now
than it ever has before.

3092056364
04:25:03.127 --> 04:25:07.426
We are fools if we do not respond.

693188757
04:25:07.427 --> 04:25:11.279
So you see, Madam Deputy Speaker,
we are not a broken country.

1274663697
04:25:11.280 --> 04:25:16.469
We are a brilliant country,
but we are a vulnerable country.

593058863
04:25:16.471 --> 04:25:18.176
We should not be energy insecure.

3279400121
04:25:18.177 --> 04:25:20.122
We should not be food insecure.

708046486
04:25:20.123 --> 04:25:24.929
We should not have the smallest
army we've had in 200 years.

624864193
04:25:24.930 --> 04:25:27.639
We should not be decoupled
from our allies in Europe.

1688362126
04:25:27.640 --> 04:25:30.552
But the good news is that we
can fix all of these things.

1133187420
04:25:31.022 --> 04:25:35.723
If we have the will, it
will mean uncomfortable

3086800875
04:25:35.724 --> 04:25:37.679
choices and changed stances from many.

2852381003
04:25:37.680 --> 04:25:39.084
But the facts have changed.

1420275292
04:25:39.085 --> 04:25:44.330
So we need to change our minds.

2782031934
04:25:44.331 --> 04:25:47.541
>> Emma Foody Madam Deputy Speaker
And I'm really pleased to be

3519931922
04:25:47.543 --> 04:25:50.503
able to speak in this debate
today on the Gracious Speech,

4058640112
04:25:50.504 --> 04:25:52.860
because this government
was elected to deliver

4067742278
04:25:52.861 --> 04:25:55.223
change and in my community for too long,

1612501019
04:25:55.224 --> 04:25:58.126
we felt at best ignored
and at worst left behind.

1926022001
04:25:58.127 --> 04:26:00.983
Decisions taken in Whitehall
in Westminster did

3438687020
04:26:00.984 --> 04:26:03.772
not address the challenges that we faced.

3628149903
04:26:03.772 --> 04:26:05.427
That investment didn't reach us.

3021577259
04:26:06.028 --> 04:26:07.581
Opportunities didn't reach us.

3376769091
04:26:07.582 --> 04:26:10.628
Frankly, Westminster didn't
hear us and the measures

2697816555
04:26:10.629 --> 04:26:13.926
in the last King's Speech
began to change that.

3978050204
04:26:13.927 --> 04:26:16.382
The English Devolution
and Community Empowerment

3566952280
04:26:16.383 --> 04:26:18.326
Bill brings decisions closer to home.

1922532560
04:26:18.328 --> 04:26:20.737
The changes to the Green
Book give us a fair go

3684763582
04:26:20.739 --> 04:26:22.945
at securing the investment
that we deserve.

3709342874
04:26:22.946 --> 04:26:25.319
Breakfast clubs and free school meals

2155748288
04:26:25.320 --> 04:26:27.227
set of children not just for the day,

4050902098
04:26:27.228 --> 04:26:29.286
but to give them the best start in life.

1586974658
04:26:29.287 --> 04:26:33.475
We're starting the process of bringing
buses back into public control.

2456162788
04:26:33.476 --> 04:26:35.782
Public services are
showing signs of recovery

1541713348
04:26:36.028 --> 04:26:37.682
following 14 years of austerity,

3827092736
04:26:37.683 --> 04:26:40.176
and this king's speech builds on that.

3934021665
04:26:40.177 --> 04:26:43.339
But we must deliver more
and we must deliver it faster.

1946610747
04:26:43.340 --> 04:26:46.276
In today's debate is rightly about energy.

2604743888
04:26:46.277 --> 04:26:49.278
And recently I visited
the port of Blyth in my hon.

1982909544
04:26:49.279 --> 04:26:52.136
Friend the Member for Ashington
and Blythe constituency,

2318396622
04:26:52.137 --> 04:26:53.692
and I heard about their vision

1261534327
04:26:53.693 --> 04:26:56.726
and the jobs and the opportunities
that the renewables

4058354554
04:26:56.727 --> 04:26:58.431
sector is already bringing there.

4060852017
04:26:58.432 --> 04:27:02.125
We have been at the mercy of
repeated international crises,

1703786455
04:27:02.126 --> 04:27:04.682
underlining why we must
secure energy independence

1763018585
04:27:04.683 --> 04:27:07.040
to protect people here
and across the country.

1544675167
04:27:07.040 --> 04:27:09.427
Previous governments didn't move quickly

2063715173
04:27:09.428 --> 04:27:11.434
enough and we are paying the price now.

733311450
04:27:11.985 --> 04:27:14.243
My region is leading
the way to build clean,

2199173095
04:27:16.027 --> 04:27:17.931
renewable energy and energy security.

2786576469
04:27:17.932 --> 04:27:20.432
New seabed site off our
coast can unlock at

1942475521
04:27:20.433 --> 04:27:23.983
least six gigawatts of offshore capacity.

2099692167
04:27:23.984 --> 04:27:27.677
That is billions of pounds of
investment coming to our region,

2069977774
04:27:27.678 --> 04:27:29.879
creating jobs and opportunity.

3038381439
04:27:29.880 --> 04:27:32.939
And in my own constituency,
the West Hartford Business Park,

2337583602
04:27:32.940 --> 04:27:36.687
with support from Arlington
and the Port of Blyth,

2362251912
04:27:36.688 --> 04:27:40.686
will unlock 2000 jobs and more than
£400 million of local investment.

748076947
04:27:40.687 --> 04:27:45.539
The Moor Farm roundabout upgrades
never knowingly not mentioned by me,

1928187846
04:27:45.540 --> 04:27:47.848
add to the sense of
possibility and acting as

3964312648
04:27:47.849 --> 04:27:50.828
a gateway to growth across the North East.

4010872595
04:27:50.829 --> 04:27:52.333
We are building futures here.

1211574557
04:27:52.334 --> 04:27:55.430
Energy Central Campus at
Blythe and the Energy campus,

3631653844
04:27:56.029 --> 04:27:58.235
the Energy Academy,
forgive me in Wallsend,

2693088987
04:27:58.236 --> 04:28:00.693
are training a new generation
of skilled workers

3715759251
04:28:00.694 --> 04:28:02.528
for the industries of the future.

385980827
04:28:02.529 --> 04:28:05.878
And when the opposition
talked down clean energy,

3749559881
04:28:05.879 --> 04:28:07.679
they are talking down opportunity.

3179438383
04:28:07.680 --> 04:28:12.486
Opposing this drive
could cost up to 17,000

1909915674
04:28:12.487 --> 04:28:14.492
jobs in our regional renewables sector.

759087794
04:28:14.493 --> 04:28:17.701
So members opposite should level
with my communities about what

3350026450
04:28:17.703 --> 04:28:20.562
their plans mean for their
jobs and their families here.

101654253
04:28:20.563 --> 04:28:23.421
Here, the Energy Independence
Bill will take us further,

841488496
04:28:23.422 --> 04:28:26.128
and I want my region at
the very heart of it.

2856741225
04:28:26.129 --> 04:28:28.035
Now, as a Labour and Co-operative MP,

3157237422
04:28:28.036 --> 04:28:30.877
I'm proud that we're
delivering community energy

1980817659
04:28:30.878 --> 04:28:33.732
and the local power plan
to ensuring that by 2030,

1896946854
04:28:33.733 --> 04:28:37.130
every community can benefit
from a local energy project,

3575555879
04:28:37.130 --> 04:28:40.530
transforming our energy
future and giving communities

3242048502
04:28:40.531 --> 04:28:42.888
a stake in clean, affordable power.

3016027924
04:28:42.889 --> 04:28:45.850
And turning to a few other
measures set out in the speech.

760652109
04:28:45.851 --> 04:28:47.828
Since being elected, I've championed

3011113587
04:28:47.829 --> 04:28:50.034
the rights of leaseholders
and freeholders.

159866069
04:28:50.035 --> 04:28:51.842
It is a huge issue in my community.

3621342865
04:28:53.028 --> 04:28:55.786
In the 60s, new towns of
Cramlington and Killingworth,

2939423081
04:28:55.787 --> 04:28:58.447
many homes were built as
little and too many are now

3583477809
04:28:58.448 --> 04:29:01.004
trapped without the protections
that they deserve.

4227186615
04:29:01.005 --> 04:29:02.709
Similarly, our new build estates,

346374516
04:29:03.031 --> 04:29:05.489
although some of these
have been around for over

3803791519
04:29:05.490 --> 04:29:07.497
a decade and push the definition of new

606156482
04:29:07.498 --> 04:29:09.485
build still have not been adopted.

855920568
04:29:09.486 --> 04:29:12.892
And I know, I know Ministers
are passionate about ending

1853634074
04:29:12.893 --> 04:29:15.147
these injustices
and putting the protections

225779115
04:29:15.148 --> 04:29:17.307
that are needed in place once and for all,

3867817812
04:29:17.308 --> 04:29:19.835
and also building on the work of my hon.

904190278
04:29:19.836 --> 04:29:22.543
Friend the Member for
Washington and Gateshead South.

769404468
04:29:22.544 --> 04:29:23.696
Around ticket touting.

3362459043
04:29:23.697 --> 04:29:25.885
Since being elected, I've worked alongside

1593909151
04:29:25.886 --> 04:29:28.940
the Co-operative Party calling for action

2649072420
04:29:28.941 --> 04:29:31.648
to tackle ticket touts
and price gouging for culture,

2521413342
04:29:31.650 --> 04:29:33.003
music and sporting events.

4242623193
04:29:33.004 --> 04:29:35.732
Because it's funds that
make events, whether gigs,

3039293269
04:29:35.733 --> 04:29:38.380
matches or shows and are
at the heart of these.

3920154496
04:29:38.382 --> 04:29:41.442
And too often they are robbed
of the opportunities or ripped

2652757213
04:29:41.443 --> 04:29:44.442
off through price gouging
and and touts reselling tickets.

3778519044
04:29:44.443 --> 04:29:48.335
There are many other bills in
this programme that I support,

63948487
04:29:48.336 --> 04:29:50.493
Madam Deputy Speaker that will make a real

1659354770
04:29:50.494 --> 04:29:53.241
difference in my community on housing,

3688406265
04:29:53.242 --> 04:29:55.546
education, national
security and immigration.

1942971614
04:29:55.547 --> 04:29:57.855
This King's Speech is
a programme to build on

1815501582
04:29:57.856 --> 04:30:00.062
the change that has
already been delivered,

1605937889
04:30:00.063 --> 04:30:01.568
but to go further and faster,

457512162
04:30:01.569 --> 04:30:04.287
to extend opportunity to
communities like mine,

1521118223
04:30:04.288 --> 04:30:08.137
with measures to improve the lives
at the heart of this programme,

2327729406
04:30:08.138 --> 04:30:11.489
to provide the good jobs
and opportunities of the future.

3544807910
04:30:11.490 --> 04:30:14.190
It's now time to get on with
delivering this change,

2696072272
04:30:14.191 --> 04:30:19.383
and I look forward to
supporting these measures.

2164633723
04:30:19.384 --> 04:30:21.282
>> Bob Blackman thank you.

3632242380
04:30:21.283 --> 04:30:24.432
>> Thank you, speaker,
and a pleasure to follow.

3335166972
04:30:24.433 --> 04:30:24.884
The hon.

2500534501
04:30:24.885 --> 04:30:27.732
Member for Cramlington and Killingworth.

757939878
04:30:27.733 --> 04:30:29.438
And as a scientist by background,

3192377092
04:30:29.439 --> 04:30:32.338
I welcome now the cross-party
agreement towards

2097456381
04:30:32.339 --> 04:30:36.636
nuclear power forming a key part of
our energy supply for the future.

2859907391
04:30:36.637 --> 04:30:39.528
It wasn't always the case
that that was the case,

1290016298
04:30:39.529 --> 04:30:41.183
certainly on the Labour benches.

712334669
04:30:41.183 --> 04:30:43.640
Previously there was
opposition to nuclear power

3485030438
04:30:43.641 --> 04:30:46.147
and indeed from the Liberal
Democrat backbenches.

1941269379
04:30:46.147 --> 04:30:49.490
So I'm delighted now that
we have we have agreement

1316695275
04:30:52.036 --> 04:30:53.992
that this is the positive way forward.

4232226525
04:30:53.993 --> 04:30:56.839
And indeed, the key here
is making sure we have

3302395342
04:30:56.840 --> 04:31:00.788
a mixed economy in terms of energy supply.

2975285421
04:31:00.789 --> 04:31:04.283
I welcomed, for example, the use of, of,

2088842011
04:31:04.284 --> 04:31:07.130
of solar power on the roof
of the Aspire Centre,

1894817394
04:31:07.130 --> 04:31:09.787
adjacent to the Royal National
Orthopaedic Hospital,

860245488
04:31:09.788 --> 04:31:12.243
granted by the previous
conservative government,

4187804160
04:31:12.244 --> 04:31:15.184
which means that
the supply for that centre

2748520910
04:31:15.186 --> 04:31:18.084
and the hospital is actually
contained from that,

1134152372
04:31:18.085 --> 04:31:21.937
that solar and it contributes
towards the grid as well.

1632272893
04:31:21.938 --> 04:31:25.549
This is welcome news, but I can't
understand why the government doesn't

612787698
04:31:25.550 --> 04:31:28.838
agree to actually exploit
the North Sea to further extent.

2083340023
04:31:28.839 --> 04:31:32.351
It won't come on stream straight
away, but surely we must be thinking

2479521485
04:31:32.352 --> 04:31:36.236
about about it for the future
to cover 1 or 2 other areas.

1194730048
04:31:36.237 --> 04:31:40.433
Madam Deputy Speaker,
the Vagrancy Act is coming to an end,

2013120594
04:31:40.433 --> 04:31:42.540
but we still require from the government,

3677234621
04:31:42.540 --> 04:31:45.099
and there's no commitment
in the King's Speech for

4094697262
04:31:45.100 --> 04:31:49.432
the necessary Statutory
Instrument to make that happen.

1937109950
04:31:49.433 --> 04:31:53.045
Can we see that happen equally on
the Social Housing Renewal Bill bill?

2643845433
04:31:53.046 --> 04:31:56.439
The government's ambition
is huge but timid.

3692992570
04:31:56.440 --> 04:31:58.983
We must go faster and further to provide

3447960760
04:31:58.984 --> 04:32:00.789
the much needed social housing that

3281908188
04:32:00.790 --> 04:32:02.847
is required in this country that has not

246220032
04:32:02.848 --> 04:32:04.604
been built for more than 30 years.

3226983954
04:32:04.605 --> 04:32:07.464
And, Madam Deputy Speaker, we
live in a dangerous world.

961712012
04:32:07.465 --> 04:32:11.341
The reality is, will the war in
Ukraine causing energy price hikes?

1960326361
04:32:11.342 --> 04:32:15.288
Indeed, we must think about what
has that done for the Treasury in

3131473061
04:32:15.289 --> 04:32:19.138
terms of windfall from the petrol
pumps going into the Treasury?

3615844916
04:32:19.139 --> 04:32:21.491
But at the same time, the Treasury.

2110515281
04:32:21.492 --> 04:32:27.344
A fragile truce in the Middle East,
the war, civil war in Sudan,

2969952074
04:32:27.344 --> 04:32:29.351
where more people are being killed than

96792242
04:32:29.352 --> 04:32:32.081
anywhere else in any other conflicts,

2830261980
04:32:32.082 --> 04:32:34.339
and indeed, the half
a million Christians in

4086834341
04:32:34.340 --> 04:32:38.582
Nigeria have been massacred by Islamists.

2716850805
04:32:38.583 --> 04:32:41.290
The sad reality is, on
the 7th of October 2023,

1201755818
04:32:41.291 --> 04:32:44.584
I was absolutely appalled
that after the attempt by

4104824692
04:32:44.585 --> 04:32:47.582
Hamas to commit genocide
on the people of Israel,

3715693232
04:32:47.583 --> 04:32:52.390
we saw people celebrating on
our streets what was going on.

3240930798
04:32:52.391 --> 04:32:55.903
We then subsequently, a blind eye
was turned to the hate marches that

2332262773
04:32:58.036 --> 04:33:01.331
were assembled outside a synagogue
in London 100 yards away.

2700902200
04:33:01.332 --> 04:33:04.938
At midday, just as the Shabbat
services were coming to an end.

3057999381
04:33:04.939 --> 04:33:09.186
And that's continued week
after week after week,

2195852159
04:33:09.187 --> 04:33:11.191
with the congregation being intimidated

1372368810
04:33:11.192 --> 04:33:13.491
from going about their lawful business.

1560001065
04:33:13.492 --> 04:33:15.397
Now, the Prime Minister quite rightly

444776154
04:33:15.397 --> 04:33:17.301
talked about combating anti-Semitism,

630617096
