118372537
04:41:19.051 --> 04:41:21.357
politicians and parties
will be more focussed

4184400398
04:41:21.358 --> 04:41:23.896
on the issues that
really matter to voters.

2499132571
04:41:23.897 --> 04:41:26.545
Electoral reform is
a necessary step to ensure

3854800516
04:41:26.546 --> 04:41:29.498
a fairer society with better schools,

1959257268
04:41:29.499 --> 04:41:34.051
better hospitals, safer communities,
clean air and clean water.

2012231410
04:41:34.052 --> 04:41:37.011
The Representation of the People
Bill has the potential to

2859282393
04:41:37.012 --> 04:41:40.594
be the latest chapter in
the evolution of our democracy.

457904240
04:41:40.596 --> 04:41:42.804
Ours is a proud history
of a franchise that

2448498773
04:41:44.003 --> 04:41:45.857
has expanded across the generations,

2385188898
04:41:45.858 --> 04:41:51.491
extending the vote to an ever broader
base of people from the 1832

836710450
04:41:51.492 --> 04:41:55.750
