Representation of the People Act,

984880968
04:41:55.751 --> 04:41:58.812
which granted the right of voting
to women, to the 1969 act,

3340604211
04:41:58.813 --> 04:42:02.347
which made the UK the first democracy to

2775554585
04:42:02.348 --> 04:42:05.198
give votes to everyone 18 and above.

4292643271
04:42:05.199 --> 04:42:08.046
