2562436991
05:02:06.150 --> 05:02:08.263
Our economy and security depend on.

1386195081
05:02:08.264 --> 05:02:11.312
By legislating for
Strategic Nature network

2153318069
05:02:11.313 --> 05:02:13.919
and recognising as national
infrastructure, we can.

818468185
05:02:13.920 --> 05:02:16.629
We can restore, connect
and maintain a system of key,

367547785
05:02:16.630 --> 05:02:20.364
