747724124
06:09:54.838 --> 06:10:02.543
A foreign government and private capital
wanted to make even more money.

2051774636
06:10:02.544 --> 06:10:11.941
Closure meant 435 jobs on site
redundant 2822 supply chain jobs gone.

1766558128
06:10:11.942 --> 06:10:16.586
Local businesses who needed refinery

2601744626
06:10:16.587 --> 06:10:18.441
workers custom hammered £400 million

1880057977
06:10:18.442 --> 06:10:23.637
a year from the Scottish economy
lost Scotland's energy security,

1943772204
06:10:23.638 --> 06:10:25.591
weakened Scotland's national security,

2155460417
06:10:27.132 --> 06:10:29.236
compromised the previous Tory government,

3069323903
06:10:32.140 --> 06:10:34.795
disinterested the SNP Scottish
Government negligent.

197409321
06:10:34.796 --> 06:10:37.955
We know when essential national
infrastructure is in the hands

2818767795
06:10:37.956 --> 06:10:41.037
