1995734164
06:10:41.038 --> 06:10:44.796
their communities and our
nation's energy security will not

2422558999
06:10:44.797 --> 06:10:47.985
stand in the way of shareholders
getting their dividend.

3043616774
06:10:47.986 --> 06:10:52.736
